Given	I'm logged-in with valid credentials
And I go to Page 11 of Pelvic MRI
And I select 'Finding' radio button

When I select 'Borderline with central fat hilum' from the dropdown menu
Then 'Add new finding' button is enabled
And multiple selection localizer is enabled

When I select 'Mesorectal' and any other lymph node from the localizer
Then '12–2 o'clock' checkbox is enabled
And '2–4 o'clock' checkbox is enabled
And '4–6 o'clock' checkbox is enabled
And '6–8 o'clock' checkbox is enabled
And '8–10 o'clock' checkbox is enabled
And '10–12 o'clock' checkbox is enabled
